title: Lard Production from Federally Inspected Slaughter for United States
notes:
Series Is Presented Here As Two Variables--(1)--Original Data, 1923-1940 (2)--Original Data, 1939-1955. Data Represent Actual Production Of Rendered Lard In Federally Inspected Plants. Source: Agricultural Marketing Service, "Livestock, Meats, And Wool Market Statistics And Related Data, " 1939, P.95 And Later Issues; The Livestock And Meat Situation.

This NBER data series m01142b appears on the NBER website in Chapter 1 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter01.html.

NBER Indicator: m01142b
